OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,FControversial plans to close a
OL,8,Fchildren's A&E service have been
OL,9,Fapproved as a group of NHS trusts look
OL,10,Fto consolidate their offerings in one
OL,11,Fcentral 24-hour location.
OL,13,FThe decision to combine adult and
OL,14,Fchildren's accident and emergency will
OL,15,Fsee Ormskirk Hospital's services close
OL,16,Fand move to Southport - around eight
OL,17,Fmiles away.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,FThe proposals were approved at a
OL,8,Fheated meeting held by the Integrated
OL,9,FCare Boards which cover Merseyside and
OL,10,FLancashire, on 13 March.
OL,12,FThe meeting was adjourned for around
OL,13,F15 minutes after a member of the
OL,14,Fpublic disrupted the discussions with
OL,15,Ftheir objections to the decision.
OL,17,FHealth bosses say it will allow for a
OL,18,Fcontinuous 24-hour service, making it
OL,19,Fsafer for both age groups to be
OL,20,Ftreated on just one site.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,FThe move is expected to cost #33
OL,8,Fmillion and take five years to
OL,9,Fcomplete.
OL,11,FThe Labour MP for West Lancashire
OL,12,FAshley Dalton has said she is
OL,13,F"incredibly disappointed" with the
OL,14,Fdecision made, and will be calling on
OL,15,Fthe Health and Social Care Secretary
OL,16,FWes Streeting to reverse it.
OL,18,FShe said: "I do not believe this
OL,19,Fdecision is in the best interests of
OL,20,Fthe local community.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,F"The independent report on the
OL,8,Fconsultation clearly stated that
OL,9,F'across nearly all questions, the
OL,10,FOrmskirk option is vieweed more
OL,11,Fpositively by the overall respondent
OL,12,Fpopulation.'"
OL,14,FThe announcement comes after a
OL,15,Fconsultation period in which locals
OL,16,Fwere asked for their thoughts on the
OL,17,Fproposal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,FDuring the consultation, another
OL,8,Foption presented was moving
OL,9,FSouthport's Accident and Emergency to
OL,10,FOrmskirk and extending the current
OL,11,Fchildren's A&E to 24 hours.
OL,13,FThis would have cost #91 million,
OL,14,Finvolved the transfer of seven
OL,15,Fservices including critical care, and
OL,16,Ftaken seven years to complete.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,FCurrently adults are treated at
OL,8,FSouthport and Formby District General
OL,9,FHospital, while children's are seen in
OL,10,FA&E at Ormskirk and District General
OL,11,FHospital.
OL,13,FMore than 7,840 people engaged in the
OL,14,Fconsultation, through surveys, events,
OL,15,Fwritten submissions and targeted
OL,16,Foutreach.
OL,18,FDespite the higher costs, the option
OL,19,Fof moving all services to Ormskirk was
OL,20,Fthe most popular option during the
OL,21,Fpublic consultation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,FAt a public meeting in Ormskirk in
OL,8,FSeptember 2025, residents expressed
OL,9,Ftheir concerns to NHS bosses.
OL,11,FOne local said: "I've got two little
OL,12,Fones, another on the way, I want to be
OL,13,Fclose to a children's A&E. I don't
OL,14,Fwant it to move."
OL,16,FAnother added: "Moving services away
OL,17,Ffrom Ormskirk Hospital is going to
OL,18,Fmake Ormskirk Hospital case to stay as
OL,19,Fa viable unit weaker."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,FHowever, the trusts say where each
OL,8,Frespondent lived seemed to be the
OL,9,Fbiggest factor in their preference.
OL,11,FThose living near Southport and Formby
OL,12,F"overwhelmingly prefer" the Southport
OL,13,Foption, while those living in West
OL,14,FLancashire "overwhelmingly prefer" the
OL,15,FOrmskirk option.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,FA joint committee of NHS trusts
OL,8,FShaping Care Together says change is
OL,9,Fneeded because they are facing five
OL,10,Fmajor pressures on services: people
OL,11,Fare living longer and need more care,
OL,12,Fgetting and keeping staff, maintaining
OL,13,Fhigh standards of care, having
OL,14,Fbuildings that meet patients needs and
OL,15,Fhaving enough money.
OL,17,FDr Kate Clark from Mersey and West
OL,18,FLancashire Hospitals NHS Trust said:
OL,19,F"We are not closing, we are trying to
OL,20,Fgive better provision.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,F"It might not be in the same place but
OL,8,Fat the moment we have children who
OL,9,Fhave to go significantly further away
OL,10,Fif they become unwell overnight and
OL,11,Fneed an A&E. We want to be able to
OL,12,Fprovide that 24 hours a day."
OL,14,FAnnouncing the decision, Craig Harris,
OL,15,Fchief commissioning officer at NHS
OL,16,FLancashire and South Cumbria, said:
OL,17,F"There is active investment planned
OL,18,Ffor (Ormskirk Hospital) and it's vital
OL,19,Fto remember that currently 86% of
OL,20,Factivity is not A&E.
OL,26,@zD@EpmzD@Wpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773601892
OL,3,CControversial plans to close
OL,4,Cchildren's A&E go ahead as services
OL,5,Cconsolidated
OL,7,F"We have conducted a fully robust pre-
OL,8,Fconsultation engagement and subsequent
OL,9,Fconsultation process, which was
OL,10,Fthoroughly considered before making a
OL,11,Fdecision. I would like to thank
OL,12,Feveryone who has taken the time to
OL,13,Fparticipate in all of the engagement
OL,14,Fand consultation activities."
OL,16,FOrmskirk's Children A&E services
OL,17,Fcurrently only operates between 8am
OL,18,Fand midnight due to a lack of staff.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
